{{Infobox graduate school | name = Paris Graduate School of Digital Innovation | native_name = École pour l'informatique et les nouvelles technologies (EPITECH) | image = Epitech.png | image_size = 220px | established = {{start date|1999}} | chancellor = [[Emmanuel Carli]] | motto = The school of expertise in computer science | type = Private institution of [[higher education]] in general [[Computer Science]] | city = [[Le Kremlin-Bicêtre]], [[Bordeaux]], [[Rennes]], [[Marseille]], [[Lille]], [[Lyon]], [[Montpellier]], [[Nancy, France|Nancy]], [[Nantes]], [[Nice]], [[Strasbourg]], [[Toulouse]], [[Saint-André, Réunion]], [[Barcelona]], [[Tirana]] | country = {{FRA}}, {{ESP}}, {{ALB}}[http://www.epitech.al www.epitech.al] | coor = {{coord|48|48|55|N|2|21|47|E|type:edu_region:FR|display=inline, title}} | level = Postgraduate | students = 5,000 | parent = [[IONIS Education Group]]<ref>[http://www.ionis-group.com/en/#ecoles-epitech Epitech-Transforming computer science passion into expertise]</ref> | website = {{url|epitech.eu}} }}
[[File:ISEG - Epitech Strasbourg.JPG|thumb|EPITECH Strasbourg.]] The '''Paris Graduate School of Digital Innovation''' ({{lang-fr|École pour l'informatique et les nouvelles technologies}}, or '''Epitech'''), formerly '''European Institute of Information Technology''' in English<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.ecole-ingenieur.com/ecole/epitech-paris-ecole-informatique-les-nouvelles-technologies-1703/ EPITECH Paris — Ecole pour l’informatique et les nouvelles technologies]</ref> is a private institution of [[higher education]] in general [[computer science]] that was founded in 1999<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.dimension-ingenieur.com/epitech-ecole-de-l-expertise-informatique/1/5/0/293/ EPITECH: l’Ecole de l'Expertise Informatique]</ref> and has been [[Commission Nationale de la Certification Professionnelle|accredited by the French State]].<ref name="legifrance">{{cite web| date=10 August 2009| title=Arrêté du 10 juillet 2009 portant reconnaissance par l'État de l'École pour l'informatique et les nouvelles technologies| location=France | language=French| url=http://www.legifrance.gouv.fr/affichTexte.do?cidTexte=JORFTEXT000020979368 | accessdate=10 October 2013 | publisher=[Legifrance.gouv.fr] }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.cio-online.com/actualites/lire-l-epitech-est-desormais-reconnue-par-l-etat-2366.html | title=L'Epitech est désormais reconnue par l'Etat |language=fr}}</ref>
Headquartered in [[Le Kremlin-Bicêtre]], south of [[Paris]], the school has campuses in [[Bordeaux]], [[Rennes]], [[Marseille]], [[Lille]], [[Lyon]], [[Montpellier]], [[Nancy, France|Nancy]], [[Nantes]], [[Nice]], [[Strasbourg]], [[Toulouse]] and [[Saint-André, Réunion]].<ref name="journaldunet.com">{{fr icon}} [http://www.journaldunet.com/solutions/emploi-rh/grandes-ecoles-informatiques-francaises/epitech.shtml Epitech: des stages en entreprise de 3 jours par semaine]</ref><ref name="journaldunet.com" /> The school also has a location in [[Barcelona]](Spain)<ref>(in Spanish)[http://www.epitech.eu/es EPITECH : escuela superior de informática]</ref>, [[Tirana]], [[Albania]].<ref>[http://www.academyplus.eu EPITECH]</ref>
At the end of the five-year course, students receive the title of "Expert of Information Technologies" <ref>http://www.epitech.eu/blogs/diplome-epitech-homologue-niveau1-bac-5-art445.html</ref> who is recognized by French [[Commission Nationale de la Certification Professionnelle|CNCP]].<ref>http://www.letudiant.fr/etudes/ecole-ingenieur/ma-vie-detudiant-en-ecole-dinformatique-selon-zeid-en-3e-annee-a-epitech-13172/apres-epitech-quelle-insertion-professionnelle-17157.html</ref> This professional certification should not be confused in France with a degree of master (like an engineering diploma or a master diploma of public french universities)<ref>http://www.cci-paris-idf.fr/formation/orientation-jeunes/reussir-son-orientation-professionnelle/comment-savoir-diplome-reconnu-par-etat-ou-entreprises-formation</ref>.
The school has the particularity to teach with practical cases instead of theoretical.<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.lemonde.fr/orientation-scolaire/article/2011/05/13/informatique-et-internet-nouveaux-profils-recherches_1520513_1473696.html Informatique et Internet: nouveaux profils recherchés]</ref>. Epitech has also an [[Executive MBA]] in IT and [[entrepreneurship]] course targeting executive managers in computer science.<ref>{{fr}}[http://www.developpez.com/actu/55843/Executive-MBA-d-Epitech-ouverture-des-inscriptions-pour-tous-les-professionnels-prochaine-reunion-d-information-sur-ce-nouveau-MBA-le-6-juin/ Executive MBA EPITECH]</ref>
The institution is part of [[IONIS Education Group]].
== History ==
Epitech was created in 1999, taking advantage of the keen interest of the ''[[École Pour l'Informatique et les Techniques Avancées]]'' to train students with a specific interest for computer sciences related matter only.
In 2007, Epitech opened new campuses in [[Casablanca]], [[Dalian]], [[Bordeaux]], [[Lille]], [[Lyon]], [[Nantes]], [[Strasbourg]] and [[Toulouse]]. Since January 2008, the degree delivered has been recognized by the ''[[Commission nationale de la certification professionnelle]]'',<ref name="arrete">{{cite web| title=Arrêté du 16 janvier 2008 portant enregistrement au répertoire national des certifications professionnelles | location=France | language=French| url=http://www.legifrance.gouv.fr/affichTexte.do;jsessionid=FADF1CA86320AE687B52F19AB774F9F8.tpdjo13v_3?cidTexte=JORFTEXT000017981284&categorieLien=id | date=24 January 2008 | accessdate=10 October 2013 | publisher=[Legifrance.gouv.fr] }}</ref> as [[Nomenclature des niveaux de formation|level 1]].<ref>[http://www.rncp.cncp.gouv.fr/grand-public/visualisationFiche?format=fr&fiche=5588 Le Répertoire National des Certifications Professionnelles (RNCP) - Résumé descriptif de la certification]</ref> In 2008, the campuses of [[Nice]], [[Montpellier]], [[Nancy, France|Nancy]], [[Marseille]] and [[Rennes]] were opened. Since 2009, the school has been recognized by France.<ref name="legifrance" />
=== New campuses abroad === In early 2013, Epitech announced it would open a campus in [[Beijing]], [[China]] in September 2013 and further international branches in [[California]], [[United Kingdom]] and [[Spain]] by September 2014.<ref>{{cite web |title=Le groupe d'enseignement privé Ionis s'ancre à l'international |url=http://www.lemondeinformatique.fr/actualites/lire-le-groupe-d-enseignement-prive-ionis-s-ancre-a-l-international-52506.html |date=15 February 2013 |accessdate=20 January 2016}}</ref>{{update after|2016|1}}
== Partnership == EPITECH has partnered with the ''Zup de Co'' association to create the ''[[Web@cademie]]'', a 2-year training completely free for students without the [[French Baccalaureate]] and with a strong motivation in [[computer science]].<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://pro.01net.com/editorial/588287/la-web-academie-accueille-sa-troisieme-promotion-d-eleves-decrocheurs/ La Web Académie accueille sa troisième promotion d’élèves « décrocheurs »]</ref> This course has the goal to attain a job of [[software developer]] for young people who have stopped their regular studies.<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.lemouv.fr/diffusion-une-ecole-unique-en-france-la-web-academie Une école unique en France: la "web académie"]</ref> They are trained by EPITECH teachers at [[Le Kremlin-Bicêtre]]<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.liberation.fr/societe/0101645556-l-ecole-qui-reconnecte-les-decrocheurs L'école qui reconnecte les décrocheurs]</ref> and in [[Lyon]].<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.digischool.fr/formation/la-webcademie-ouvrira-ses-portes-a-lyon-en-avril-2013-13694.php La Web@cademie ouvrira ses portes à Lyon en avril 2013]</ref>
== Diploma == At the end of the five-year course, students receive the title of "Expert of Information Technologies" <ref>http://www.epitech.eu/blogs/diplome-epitech-homologue-niveau1-bac-5-art445.html</ref> who is recognized by French [[Commission Nationale de la Certification Professionnelle|CNCP]].<ref>http://www.letudiant.fr/etudes/ecole-ingenieur/ma-vie-detudiant-en-ecole-dinformatique-selon-zeid-en-3e-annee-a-epitech-13172/apres-epitech-quelle-insertion-professionnelle-17157.html</ref> Because the school is not certified by the [[Commission des Titres d'Ingénieur]], this professional certification should not be confused in France with a degree of master (like an engineering diploma or a master diploma of public french universities)<ref>http://www.cci-paris-idf.fr/formation/orientation-jeunes/reussir-son-orientation-professionnelle/comment-savoir-diplome-reconnu-par-etat-ou-entreprises-formation</ref>.
