==Broadcast==
In [[Australia]], the series premiered on [[National Geographic Channel (Australia)|National Geographic Channel]] on April 27, 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://community.foxtel.com.au/t5/Foxtel-Blog/NEW-THIS-WEEK-Apr-27-Australia-s-Next-Top-Model-StarTalk-Hart-Of/ba-p/64501|title=NEW THIS WEEK (Apr 27): Australia’s Next Top Model, StarTalk, Hart Of Dixie, #MayPac and more|publisher=The Green Room|date=23 April 2015|accessdate=16 July 2015}}</ref>

==In popular culture==

On August 27, 2015, [[20th Century Fox]] released a viral video advertisement for the movie ''[[The Martian (film)|The Martian]]'', taking the form of a special episode of ''StarTalk'', with Tyson discussing the fictional Ares 3 mission from the film.<ref>{{cite news | last=Bradley | first=Laura | url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2015/08/28/neil_degrasse_tyson_explains_ridley_scott_s_the_martian_s_science_video.html | title=Neil deGrasse Tyson Soothingly Explains the Science Behind ''The Martian'' | date=August 28, 2015 | accessdate=September 1, 2015 }}</ref>

